X\in\Re^{k\times t} 
 2div(G(\nabla H_{u,v}\nabla H_{u,v}^\top)\nabla H_{u,v}) 
G = (v_1, ... v_n)diag(\lambda_1^*, ..., \lambda_n^*)(v_1^\top, ... v_n^\top)\top
 \ \ \lambda_i = \begin{cases}1, & \mbox{
 > threshold} \\ g(|\nabla H_{u,v}|^2), &\mbox{otherwise} \end{cases}
g(s^2) = \frac{1}{\sqrt{1+s^2/\lambda '^2}}
\lambda ' = 2.5
\nabla H_{u,v} = \begin{pmatrix} R_{u,v}(0,1) \\ R_{u,v}(1,0) \\ ...\\ R_{u,v}(m,n)\end{pmatrix}
R_{u,v}(m,n) = \frac{X(u,v) -  X(u+m,u+n)}{\sqrt{m^2+n^2}}
X \in R^{k\times t}
m \in \{-2,...,2\}, n \in \{-2,..., 2\}
